<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-71-0930 </DOCNO><TEXT>Korea, as a recipient of nuclear technology transfer, has good experienceof progressively building up its indigeneous capability of nuclear technologythrough three stages of technology transfer, namely: technology transferunder the turnkey approach, component approach, and integrated technologytransfer with a local prime contractor. Here, each stage of experienceof technology transfer, with Korea as a recipient, is presented.</TEXT></DOC>